@item
@code{ebib-extras-google-scholar}: Google Scholar.
@item
@code{ebib-extras-wikipedia}: Wikipedia.
@item
@code{ebib-extras-goodreads}: Goodreads.
@item
@code{ebib-extras-audible}: Audible.
