@node Search and download function lists
@section Search and download function lists

@vindex ebib-extras-search-book-functions
@vindex ebib-extras-download-book-functions
@vindex ebib-extras-search-article-functions
@vindex ebib-extras-download-article-functions
@vindex ebib-extras-search-film-functions
@vindex ebib-extras-download-film-functions
These constants define which search commands are invoked for each supertype when searching or downloading:

@itemize
